PN,42401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1780441387
OL,3,CFamily of teenager swept to sea
OL,4,Cquestion emergency response at inquest
OL,6,FThe family of a teenager who died
OL,7,Fafter being swept into sea at North
OL,8,FTyneside last year have questioned
OL,9,Fwhether opportunities 'may not have
OL,10,Fbeen taken' around the wider, co-
OL,11,Fordinated emergency response to the
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,FA statement was read aloud on their
OL,15,Fbehalf at an inquest into the death of
OL,16,F13 year old Edie Smart. She died on
OL,17,Fthe 28th of July 2025, four days after
OL,18,Fbeing pulled from the water off the
OL,19,Fcoast at Whitley Bay.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
